{
  "stem": "19055.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 263.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, and our being together was harmonious, in spite of the difficulties.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this is the time for me to, to mention charitable, good Christians who came at night and knocked on our boarded window.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They said, open the window.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We brought you some food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they brought milk and bread and, and some fruit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were really risking their life or, or freedom, because the gendarmerie was outside.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was-- by death penalty-- was forbidden for Christians to, to help out Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That gave us some consolation that there were good people among the bad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there were good seeds.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] and we spent some time in, in this ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Many of the fathers had been taken to, to camps, ordered by the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So there were mainly women and children and some men, like my father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "One day, with our-- on the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we hear humming of planes very high up in the air.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we looked outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "As a, a child, I was absolutely fascinated by this, of hundreds and hundreds of little, silvery, shiny planes in formation were flying east.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "As I learned later, they were flying Liberators, or B-17s.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were flying to Ploiesti, to Romania, to bomb the oil fields, hundreds and hundreds of them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we knew they were Americans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And if I could describe this to you, what, what it feels to a child [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] to look up and see friends.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't want to get emotional, but it can happen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] One day, the captain of the gendarmerie who was also a mensch told us that I'm afraid that soon, you're going to be taken away from here.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
